title APPLICATION FORM
.container-fluid
  .jumbotron.text-center
    | UNITED NATIONS STAFF 1% FOR DEVELOPMENT FUND
  nav.navbar.default
    .navbar-header
      // Button for user to collapse or uncollapse the navbar
      button.navbar-toggle(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#navLinks')
        span Menu
    ul#navLinks.nav.navbar-nav.text-center
      li
        a(href='#') About
      li
        a(href='#') Home
      li
        a(href='#') Become a Member
      li
        a(href='#') Projects
      li
        a(href='#') How to Apply
      li
        a(href='#') Application Form
      li
        a(href='#') FAQ
      li
        a(href='#') Contact
  if errors 
    ul
      for error in errors
        li!= error.msg
  div
    h1 APPLICATION FORM
  div   
  form(action='/formen', method='post')
    .form-group
      label(for='emailaddress') Email Address
      input#exampleFormControlInput1.form-control(type='text', name='email', placeholder='name@example.com' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.email))
    .form-group
      label(for='question') Question 1: The title of your project
      input#input-element.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='title' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.title))
    .form-group
      label(for='question') Question 2: What country is this project in?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='country' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.country))
    .form-group
      label(for='question')
        | Question 3: What is the exact location of the project within the country (village, neighbourhood, district, province)?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='region' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.region))
    .form-group
      label(for='question') Question 4: What is the cost of this project(in US dollars)? 
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='cost' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.costInDollars))
    .form-group
      label(for='question') Question 5: What is being requested from the 1% Fund? From other sources? 
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='specificrequest' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.specificRequest))
    .form-group
      label(for='question')
        | Question 6:  What is the total budget? How will that budget be used and allocated?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='fundingallocation' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.fundingAllocation))
    .form-group
      label(for='question')
        | Question 7: Who is going to carry out the project? Will there be hired labourers or salaried experts?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='seven' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.questionSeven))
    .form-group
      label(for='question')
        | Question 8: Who is preparing and submitting this request? Who will benefit from the project (also approximately how many people)?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='eight' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.questionEight))
    .form-group
      label(for='question') Question 9: On whose initiative is the project being started?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='nine' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.questionNine))
    .form-group
      label(for='question')
        | Question 10: What is the present situation that the project seeks to improve? Why is the project necessary?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='ten' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.questionTen))
    .form-group
      label(for='question')
        | Question 11:  What is the aim of the project? What does the project hope to achieve?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='eleven' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.questionEleven))
    .form-group
      label(for='question') Question 12: Who are the people that will benefit from the project?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='twelve' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.questionTwelve))
    .form-group
      label(for='question') Question 13: How many people (approximately) will benefit from the project?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='thirteen' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.questionThirteen))
    .form-group
      label(for='question')
        | Question 14: What resources will come from the local community and beneficiaries?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='fourteen' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.questionFourteen))
    .form-group
      label(for='question')
        | Question 15: Who is responsible for the project? With whom will the 1% Fund maintain contact (name, address)?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='fifteen' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.questionFifteen))
    .form-group
      label(for='question') Question 16: How will the results or achievements of the project be measured?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='sixteen' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.questionSixteen))
    .form-group
      label(for='question')
        | Question 17: What is the banking information required for payment (bank account number, account holder, bank name, bank address)?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='seventeen' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.questionSeventeen))
    .form-group
      label(for='question') Question 18: The Organization&rsquo;s registration with local government?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='eighteen' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.questionEighteen))
    .form-group
      label(for='question') Any other comments?
      input#exampleFormControlTextarea1.form-control(rows='3', type='text', name='comment' value=(undefined===application ? '' : application.comment))
    button.btn.btn-primary(type='submit') Submit Application
